---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 337
  - Title: Ecclesiasticus
    Location: XXXVIII 25,39
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=Concerning Right Vocation
    or ‘Dharma'
  - 329
---
The wisdom of a scribe cometh by his time of leisure： and he that is
less in action, shall receive wisdom. ...

But they (the craftsmen) shall strengthen the state of the world, and
their prayer shall be in the work of their craft.
